            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-eae24cf09444b567-f09fcd twpub-eae24cf09444b567-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
